{"tid":2399734,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求法律巴絲解答]阿媽幾次超市偷野俾人拉左","createTime":"2021-02-08T11:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T04:01:48.000Z","uid":219337,"like":4,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9d5efa370809fc0aca9ef4956dcaca25d0508b","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"今次我阿媽係第4次俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n早幾日上完庭個法官要拎感化報告再有判刑, 咁之後諗住再搵當值律師果日幫手辯護, 但係睇完我阿媽本存摺話過左入息審查(有部份錢係我過左身既阿爸淨落黎係我阿媽戶口入面), 要自己出去搵律師<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位,如果我阿媽過幾日再去搵當值律師俾報稅單佢睇會唔會有機會過到入息審查(唔知睇存摺果時會唔會已經記錄左唔批)<br />\n<br />\n如果到最後都係唔批, 判刑果日無律師幫手有冇問題, 我唔知可以去邊到搵律師<br />\n<br />\n阿媽已經知錯, 因為話有機會入獄, 希望咁多位幫手解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed506f3446353fd8111c83ef19cca8d9abcc9d2d","tid":2399734,"uid":129378,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"不如自己求情，反正都已經認左罪"},{"pid":"3c9bc1b19fe6ca7d3ff3364f7bb08fe2f002b8c1","tid":2399734,"uid":366655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"成日偷野 係咪有精神病"},{"pid":"19066ac1af08d79f99ad7a801cb2302b6c368671","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ed506f3446353fd8111c83ef19cca8d9abcc9d2d","tid":2399734,"uid":129378,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"不如自己求情，反正都已經認左罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"但如果無律師會唔會無咁穩陣<br />\n我怕阿媽答錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2d252773bdb217b2d9d5961cbb08f11d1f8e88","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"3c9bc1b19fe6ca7d3ff3364f7bb08fe2f002b8c1","tid":2399734,"uid":366655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"成日偷野 係咪有精神病"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"佢以為淨係罸錢或者緩刑唔會判入獄"},{"pid":"67cd5183079a926db1c685c266658eb25387c4e6","tid":2399734,"uid":306536,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"衰1次就話姐，衰4次先話知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ab0e2a533ee3bdba4a5bafd94787a3b0d3b142","tid":2399734,"uid":55386,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"67cd5183079a926db1c685c266658eb25387c4e6","tid":2399734,"uid":306536,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"衰1次就話姐，衰4次先話知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n叫你呀媽入去羅湖坐下冷靜下啦"},{"pid":"599ea9c4e373e3ae611163ec08ca1d932b816daf","tid":2399734,"uid":6310,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"1a2d252773bdb217b2d9d5961cbb08f11d1f8e88","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"3c9bc1b19fe6ca7d3ff3364f7bb08fe2f002b8c1","tid":2399734,"uid":366655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"成日偷野 係咪有精神病"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"佢以為淨係罸錢或者緩刑唔會判入獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"偷多幾次啦咁 唔使負責任架 偷貴啲啦"},{"pid":"bcea2beb2ad7bd9edca0a206f5450bb0985c4ce1","tid":2399734,"uid":288675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"由佢坐 唔係只有第5次"},{"pid":"50db9504259223cb2168747f050029f492a2a6d1","tid":2399734,"uid":3598,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"俾人捉到就4次，捉唔到都唔知幾多次，俾佢入去坐啦"},{"pid":"aad664102de0b3991bb32ca7b513eb89595d84c9","tid":2399734,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"19066ac1af08d79f99ad7a801cb2302b6c368671","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ed506f3446353fd8111c83ef19cca8d9abcc9d2d","tid":2399734,"uid":129378,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"不如自己求情，反正都已經認左罪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"但如果無律師會唔會無咁穩陣<br />\n我怕阿媽答錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"有冇律師都一樣㗎啦,人哋控方都可以chok你老母."},{"pid":"4284747d3ec999539573a4d927a1c304d07357e4","tid":2399734,"uid":287326,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"入去食皇家飯都算係偷政府錢"},{"pid":"54457bb22bb04abf7a303cdf1731cd29f189d53b","tid":2399734,"uid":33004,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"第四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算鳩數啦  <br />\n偷到有癮唔會改到<br />\n除非俾人打到隻手殘廢"},{"pid":"41b485423abfe98db9067e1ab2f618f124beaf34","tid":2399734,"uid":2546,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"唔俾個教訓佢學唔到野㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有案底或者坐過監對佢份工作有無影響？<br />\n如果無工作既真係要由得佢坐下<br />\n針唔拮到肉唔知痛<br />\n你就寄望佢出返黎可以學精 唔好再偷野<br />\n根本係個性格有問題 唔係因為只係罰錢所以先偷野 係佢覺得偷野無問題無後果 唔好倒轉黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675ead77d2307e79a66d79b92175f49dd806ec13","tid":2399734,"uid":158499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"有偷野癮，冇計架喎，呢啲要靠自己克服，接受下懲罰先啦"},{"pid":"319f6adbd2e2060429a1c920d588edf7768ceed1","tid":2399734,"uid":8566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:56:35.000Z","msg":"想知你啊媽頭3次判咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw你啊媽肯定有病態啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0871493cbb932bf5a232b6e0314ee5b8abddc8","tid":2399734,"uid":165336,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"1a2d252773bdb217b2d9d5961cbb08f11d1f8e88","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":