,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"NQ即係咩？可以去邊度搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7346c7b9ea3f681596ffe8b9ad7e7d9c86275e37","tid":2399734,"uid":254040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"根本係心癮黎，我老豆以前個老細好有錢，身家億億聲衣食無憂，但佢個仔就好鐘意周圍去偷野，佢老豆唯有請人24小時監控佢，有一次係屋企，佢偷偷地爬窗出去偷野俾人拉左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44a127f829be6a56e014964799e2b0eb2a716d2","tid":2399734,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"599ea9c4e373e3ae611163ec08ca1d932b816daf","tid":2399734,"uid":6310,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"1a2d252773bdb217b2d9d5961cbb08f11d1f8e88","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"3c9bc1b19fe6ca7d3ff3364f7bb08fe2f002b8c1","tid":2399734,"uid":366655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"成日偷野 係咪有精神病"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"佢以為淨係罸錢或者緩刑唔會判入獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"偷多幾次啦咁 唔使負責任架 偷貴啲啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"去錯地方，美國加州真係唔使坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230ef27080a19eaf29aa215c92796925cc91d454","tid":2399734,"uid":123696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a2d252773bdb217b2d9d5961cbb08f11d1f8e88","tid":2399734,"uid":219337,"like":1,"dislike":38,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"3c9bc1b19fe6ca7d3ff3364f7bb08fe2f002b8c1","tid":2399734,"uid":366655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"成日偷野 係咪有精神病"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"佢以為淨係罸錢或者緩刑唔會判入獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"唔好同個官咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺邊區 好睇坐第一庭嗰個官係邊個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般見你偷咁多次都會判監<br />\n你係官都唔想見人偷嘢無後果啦<br />\n當值律師唔批就自己畀錢請啦<br />\n呢啲錢唔好慳"},{"pid":"fc19a04537fd5988557c1d734609e13d0c056e4f","tid":2399734,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7346c7b9ea3f681596ffe8b9ad7e7d9c86275e37","tid":2399734,"uid":254040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"根本係心癮黎，我老豆以前個老細好有錢，身家億億聲衣食無憂，但佢個仔就好鐘意周圍去偷野，佢老豆唯有請人24小時監控佢，有一次係屋企，佢偷偷地爬窗出去偷野俾人拉左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"你老豆個仔即係你或者你兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d61022ee72d24ffe8c47660c2e3fabeea5927b","tid":2399734,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc19a04537fd5988557c1d734609e13d0c056e4f","tid":2399734,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7346c7b9ea3f681596ffe8b9ad7e7d9c86275e37","tid":2399734,"uid":254040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"根本係心癮黎，我老豆以前個老細好有錢，身家億億聲衣食無憂，但佢個仔就好鐘意周圍去偷野，佢老豆唯有請人24小時監控佢，有一次係屋企，佢偷偷地爬窗出去偷野俾人拉左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"你老豆個仔即係你或者你兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"重睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e278ed239069e9d22dc7d10481930f07af4254","tid":2399734,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"出嚟行唔撚使還啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"f5ca06647d01cac2883fa5852480459be1e80a26","tid":2399734,"uid":254040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q